name: (pre-order)High Demand - Take Off Your Disguise w/ Bonus Acoustic track
description:
The Indie Rockers from Pontypridd are set the release there debut single "Take Off Your Disguise" with Man Over Records on February 4th. This is a Limited run!!! Once thay have gone there will be no more printed. Make sure you pre-order your before its to late!!


High Demand have played shows with the likes of "The Blackout, The Automatic, Stright Lines, Tiger Please & Cuba Cuba" 

Single Review 

Pontypridd Pop Rock band High Demand burst onto the South Wales music scene with an impressive first single entitled “Take Off Your Disguise” powerful punching drums and tasty riffs and the odd sing along of “Hey, Hey” makes it an enjoyable experience for your ears. This debut single should steer them in the right direction and move them a step closer to the elite of welsh bands such as Tiger Please who they have recently already supported.

3.5/5

Released 4th February on Man Over Records and available to purchase on iTunes.
